               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa taklil “Book of the Marriage Ritual” (fols. 1ra-40ra)
 -
                     Prayers on the clothes (fols. 1ra-12va l.3)
 - Prayers on the bride and the
                     bridegroom (fols. 12va l.4-42va l.2)
 - Order to be read to the bride and
                     the bridegroom (fols. 42va l.2-45rb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>Maṣḥafa taklil</title>
                     <note>For the text of the Ethiopian ritual of Matrimony s. M. CHAÎNE (ed.), “Le
                        Rituel éthiopien – Rituel de la confirmation et du mariage”, Bessarione 29,
                        1913, 255-83; THE PATRIARCHATE OF THE ETHIOPIAN ORTHODOX TÄWAḥƎDO CHURCH
                        (ed.), Maṣḥafa taklil, ‘The Book of Crowning’, Addis Abäba 1956 E.C. [1964
                        A.D.], 21994 E.C. [2001/02 A.D.].</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
               </msContents>
