                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#45ra">f. 45ra</locus>
                           <desc>-rb: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#45ra">45ra</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘሃለቃ፡ ዓብርኀ፡ ዘአጥረያ፡ በንዋዩ፡
                              ወወሐቦ፡ ለታቦተ፡ [45rb] ዮ፡ ሐንስሥ [sic]፡ ከመ፡ ይኲኖ፡ መርሃ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሠማያት፨፨</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">[<locus target="#45ra">45ra-</locus>rb]: This is a
                              book of haläqa ʿAbrǝḫa who acquired it for his money and has donated
                              it to the tabot of Yoḥannǝs, so that it might be for him a guide to
                              the Kingdom of Heaven.</quote>
                           <note> The note is written in the main hand. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- A sheet of white paper with the title of the Ms., መፅሃፈ፡
                           ተክሊል፡, is glued onto the front cover.
 - Doodle: <locus target="#47v">47v</locus>.</item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
